description.narrative: Understanding and addressing protection risks of child online (sexual) abuse not only generated invaluable knowledge and improved the respective policy framework, it also established a new frontier for future child protection work. Numerous exciting partnerships emerged with the telecommunications sector, technological think tanks, local governments and what is most remarkable - thousands of adolescents.
